================================================================================

MPVKit links against libmpv (LGPL 2.1+) and FFmpeg (LGPL 2.1+) via
pre-built xcframeworks from media-kit/libmpv-darwin-build.

These libraries are NOT covered by the GPL 3.0 license above.
They remain under their original LGPL 2.1+ licenses.

- libmpv:  https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv/blob/master/LICENSE.LGPL
- FFmpeg:  https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html

LGPL 2.1 compliance:
  - Pre-built xcframeworks are dynamically linked and can be replaced
    by the user via the download_xcframeworks.sh script.
  - Source code for libmpv and FFmpeg is available from their upstream
    repositories.
